Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:11.29,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,{TIME:670580,671290}Oh…{NOTE:おう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:19.92,Alternative,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:677760,679920}You did well, Japanese team.{NOTE:しかしよくやりました日本チーム。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:28.98,Alternative,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:682390,688980}Captain Shellenina of the Soviet team reaches out her hand to the Japanese team.{NOTE:今ソ連チームのキャプテンシェレーニナがお互いの健闘を讃え、日本チームに手を差し伸べております。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:31.77,Alternative,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{TIME:688980,691770}Ayuhara, thank you. It was a wonderful match.{NOTE:鮎原、有難う。素晴らしい試合だった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:43.20,Alternative,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:700200,703200}Although defeated, each one of the middle school girls…{NOTE:破れたりとはいえ、女子中学生の一人一人が…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:46.20,Alternative,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:703200,706200}…fought with all they had.{NOTE:…その力を出し切って戦ったのであります。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:48.12,Alternative,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:706200,708120}Well done, Japan.{NOTE:よくやった、日本チーム。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:52.33,Alternative,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:708120,712330}We must applaud them for their hard work.{NOTE:私達は彼女達の働きに拍手を送らずにはいられません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:12:03.22,Alternative,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:715250,723220}The World Women's Junior Volleyball Championship that lasted the entire last week draws its curtain.{NOTE:今ここに一週間にわたる世界女子ジュニアバレーボール選手権大会は幕を閉じようとしております。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:08.64,Alternative,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:723220,728640}Painful expression of Japanese team's captain,\NKozue Ayuhara, struggling not to cry…{NOTE:日本チームキャプテン鮎原こずえの涙をこらえた痛々しい表情が…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:13.02,Alternative,Commentator,0,0,0,,{TIME:728640,733020}…can be clearly seen here in the lights\Nof the Central Gymnasium.{NOTE:…ここセントラル体育館のライトの中にはっきり浮かび上がっております。}
Comment: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:23.74,Default,Chapter,0,0,0,,{TIME:743740,743740}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:39.67,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:757420,759670}All the sweat that sprinkled this court.{NOTE:このコートに飛び散った汗。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:42.17,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:759670,762170}All the force that hit it.{NOTE:このコートにぶつけた力。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:44.01,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:762170,764010}I won't forgive them.{NOTE:私は忘れないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:45.18,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:764010,765180}I won't.{NOTE:いつまでも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:46.22,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:765180,766220}Not ever!{NOTE:いつまでも！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:50.89,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:770180,770890}Oh?{NOTE:あら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:54.27,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:773390,774270}Cassie.{NOTE:キャシー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:55.35,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:774270,775350}Virginia.{NOTE:バージニア。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:56.23,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,{TIME:775350,776230}Ayuhara!{NOTE:鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:01.15,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:779980,781150}Cassie!{NOTE:キャシー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:08.28,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,{TIME:785320,788280}You taught us something important.{NOTE:あなた私達に教えてくれました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:13.20,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,{TIME:789870,793200}That volleyball isn't just game played for fun.{NOTE:バレーはプレイを楽しむだけのものではないことを。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:17.67,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:794410,797670}And it's not just for money.{NOTE:そしてお金のためだけでもないってこと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:18.96,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:797670,798960}You taught me that.{NOTE:教えてくれた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:21.25,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,{TIME:800000,801250}Thank you, Ayuhara.{NOTE:サンキュウ鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:26.93,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,{TIME:803170,806930}It never occurred to me until today how good it is that we have volleyball.{NOTE:今日ほどバレーをやてたこと良かったと思ったことはありません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:29.55,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:808260,809550}Thank you, Cassie.{NOTE:有難うキャシー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:31.01,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{TIME:809550,811010}Ayuhara?{NOTE:鮎原？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:32.81,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{TIME:811010,812810}Next time we meet…{NOTE:今度会う時は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:33.77,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{TIME:812810,813770}…is at Olympics, right?{NOTE:…オリンピックね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:37.73,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:816020,817730}"Next time we meet is at Olympics"?{NOTE:今度会う時はオリンピック？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:40.73,Alternative,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:819860,820730}Olympics.{NOTE:オリンピック。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:42.44,Alternative,Cassie,0,0,0,,{TIME:821570,822440}Yes.{NOTE:Yes.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:43.90,Alternative,Cassie,0,0,0,,{TIME:822440,823900}We have next chance.{NOTE:We have next chance.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:47.24,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{TIME:825990,827240}Hey.{NOTE:いや。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:51.99,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{TIME:827240,831990}We're going to Olympics next and aim for the Grand Prix.{NOTE:私達今度オリンピックに出てグランプリを目指します。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:56.25,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:833200,836250}They already forgot their victory and aim for the next prize.{NOTE:もうさきの優勝を忘れて次のチャンピオンを目指している。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:13:59.50,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:838250,839500}Cassie too?{NOTE:キャシーまで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:07.51,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:845880,847510}I won't lose to them!{NOTE:負けるもんですか、今度は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:21.06,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{TIME:857980,861060}Ah, it's Manumba from the Kenyan team.{NOTE:あ、ケニアチーム、マヌンバです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:22.07,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:861060,862070}Manumba?{NOTE:マヌンバ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:34.87,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:872620,874870}I admire how you came here after all.{NOTE:よく着てくれたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:38.92,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:874870,878920}I remember vividly how you fought calling for your homeland Kenya.{NOTE:あなたが祖国ケニアと叫んで戦った姿は今もありありと思い出す。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.76,0:14:57.43,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:891760,897430}The opponents we faced before, sometimes with burning hatred, are standing before us again.{NOTE:私達は今日まで汗にXXになって時には激しく憎しみに燃えて戦いあった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:15:00.65,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:897430,900650}But this time the players are just shaking hands.{NOTE:その選手達が今握手している。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:02.19,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:900650,902190}That's right.{NOTE:そうなんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:05.98,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:902190,905980}When the fight is over, everyone feels\Nthe same way and shakes hands with each other.{NOTE:戦いが終わればみんな同じ気持ちになって手を取り合う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:08.40,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:905980,908400}This is the essence of true sportsmanship.{NOTE:これが本当のスポーツ選手なんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:13.16,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:912280,913160}Ah?{NOTE:お？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:11.51,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:969670,971510}He's late…{NOTE:遅いわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:12.51,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:971510,972510}Hm?{NOTE:ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:14.47,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:972510,974470}I mean our coach. I wonder what's up?{NOTE:コーチよ。どうしたのかしら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:19.22,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:976140,979220}After he said it's our last tea party here in America…{NOTE:アメリカで最後のお茶の会だっていうのにさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.22,0:16:20.35,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:979220,980350}Indeed.{NOTE:そうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:27.98,Default,Johnny,0,0,0,,{TIME:986980,987980}Ayuhara!{NOTE:鮎原！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:29.78,Default,Johnny,0,0,0,,{TIME:988900,989780}Ayuhara.{NOTE:鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:35.20,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:994450,995200}Ah?{NOTE:あ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:47.84,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004210,1007840}By the way, I saw our coach talk to somebody in the lobby.{NOTE:そういえば、コーチさきロビーで誰かと話しますとった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:53.80,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009840,1013800}They seemed to be asking him for something. The coach had a very perplexed look on his face.{NOTE:何か頼まれとるらしくってコーチ難しい顔をしとったよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:55.47,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013800,1015470}Is it true, Kakinouchi-san?{NOTE:本当、垣之内さん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:56.39,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015470,1016390}It's what I saw.{NOTE:本当よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:57.93,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016390,1017930}Why do you ask, Captain?{NOTE:どうしたのキャプテン？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:17:00.01,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017930,1020010}Ah, it's nothing.{NOTE:あ、んん、何でもないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:00.81,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020010,1020810}Never mind.{NOTE:いいのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:05.48,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022810,1025480}Hey, what did they ask coach for?{NOTE:ね、コーチに何頼まれてたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:07.02,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025480,1027020}I don't really know.{NOTE:ん、それは知らん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:11.48,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027020,1031480}It'd be pretty disgraceful if I had eavesdropped on them, don't you think?{NOTE:内しとの話を盗みにいくするほどハレンチじゃないか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:14.40,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032570,1034400}Y-You're right.{NOTE:そ、それはそうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:16.61,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035570,1036610}Ah.{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:18.32,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036610,1038320}Sorry I kept you waiting.{NOTE:よ。待たせたな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:25.33,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044580,1045330}Hm?{NOTE:ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:28.33,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046080,1048330}What is it, girls? Come on, take a seat.{NOTE:どうした、皆？席について。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:29.54,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1048330,1049540}– Okay.\N– Sure.{NOTE:—はい。\\N—はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:36.51,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054760,1056510}I have a news, girls.{NOTE:実はな、皆。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:40.81,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058010,1060810}I won't be able to return to Japan with you.{NOTE:皆と一緒に日本に帰らなくなった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:42.60,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1060810,1062600}– Eh?\N– Really?{NOTE:—え？\\N—え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.60,0:17:45.10,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062600,1065100}What do you mean, Coach?{NOTE:コーチ、どういうことなんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:48.27,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065100,1068270}During the championships there have been held certain discussions.{NOTE:今回の大会中に話があった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:52.23,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068690,1072230}I was asked to coach volleyball in a certain country.{NOTE:ある国でコーチをしてくれないかとな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:54.57,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072230,1074570}I agreed just now.{NOTE:それで今しがった返事をしてきた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:56.28,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074570,1076280}I'm flying to that country tomorrow.{NOTE:明日その国へ向かうってな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:18:00.62,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1078200,1080620}– Y-You're not serious…\N– Eh.{NOTE:—そ、そんな…\\N—んん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:04.37,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082240,1084370}W-Where are you headed?{NOTE:ど、どこへ行くの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:07.87,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084370,1087870}It's a small country that has just started its adventure with volleyball.{NOTE:未だバレーを始めたばかりの小さな国だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:09.42,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087870,1089420}B-But…{NOTE:そ、そんな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:13.42,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089420,1093420}I thought we'll appear with the current squad\Nat the Olympic Games, and you'll couch us for it.{NOTE:オリンピックには又このメンバーでコーチしてもらおう思ってたのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:17.34,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095300,1097340}Oh, I'll return by then.{NOTE:あ、それまでには帰るさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:20.43,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097340,1100430}Then I'll ask you personally to let me coach you.{NOTE:そうしたらこっちから頼んでもコーチさせてもらうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:24.85,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101680,1104850}He's just like me, a madman who doesn't know a thing apart from volleyball.{NOTE:ここにもバレーしか知らないおバカさんがいるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:25.89,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104850,1105890}Not a thing…{NOTE:バレーしか知らない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:32.57,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107520,1112570}At any rate, I have to make sure that you always get capable competition.{NOTE:できれば俺は君たちに(たいこう・対抗)できるようなチームをここでも作ってやるよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:42.95,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121820,1122950}Idiot!{NOTE:バカ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:46.37,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122950,1126370}And here I was thinking we could finally start living together in Japan.{NOTE:折角一緒に日本で暮らせるって思ってたのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:47.46,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126370,1127460}Michiru.{NOTE:美智留。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.46,0:18:49.67,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127460,1129670}Volleyball is all I can do.{NOTE:俺にできるのはバレーだけなんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:53.59,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129670,1133590}I need to go wherever my only skill is needed.{NOTE:その俺を迎えてくれるところがあれば俺は行かなくちゃならん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:56.63,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134920,1136630}You'll be fine now.{NOTE:もうお前が大丈夫だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:58.63,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136630,1138630}You have good friends.{NOTE:後はいい友達がいる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:19:01.64,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138630,1141640}Friends who can encourage each other.{NOTE:お互いに励まし合える友達がな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:03.72,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141640,1143720}You're ready to stay on your own, don't you think?{NOTE:もうお前は一人でやっていけるじゃないか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:06.27,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144720,1146270}B-But…{NOTE:で、でも…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:10.10,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1148230,1150100}You're an adult now.{NOTE:もう大人だもんな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:12.52,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150100,1152520}Right? Tell me I'm not right.{NOTE:あ？そうだろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:14.73,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152520,1154730}You're mean, Bro.{NOTE:意地悪だ、兄さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:15.73,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154730,1155730}Hmm?{NOTE:ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.73,0:19:16.44,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155730,1156440}Heh.{NOTE:は。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.61,0:19:23.49,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161610,1163490}It must be nice to have an older brother.{NOTE:いいな、兄さんって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:24.53,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163490,1164530}I'm kind of jealous…{NOTE:XXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:46.89,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182340,1186890}I planned to retire from volleyball, should we lose these championships.{NOTE:俺は今度世界一になれなかったらバレーを捨てるつもりだった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:49.93,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186890,1189930}But that fixation on glory was just my own vanity.{NOTE:しかしそれこそ栄光だけを夢に見た俺の思い上がりだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:55.69,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191390,1195690}Your hard work is the reason why I ended up lending a hand to an unknown country again.{NOTE:うまくこうしてあなたに見知らぬ国へ向かうことになったのもん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:59.40,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195690,1199400}I owe it to the great fighting spirit\Nyou have for volleyball.{NOTE:あの子達のバレーに対して持っている純粋な心意気のおかげだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:04.95,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201150,1204950}You've reignited my passion.{NOTE:俺は今新しいバレーの情熱へ駆り立てられいる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:07.70,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206490,1207700}Ayuhara.{NOTE:鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:09.79,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207700,1209790}Let's meet again someday, on another court.{NOTE:またいつかコートで会おう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:48.12,Default,Johnny,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246410,1248120}Alright, there's spike.{NOTE:よし、そこのスパイク。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:50.24,Default,Johnny,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248120,1250240}Oh, wrong, you got it completely wrong.{NOTE:あ、ダメだダメだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.24,0:20:53.33,Default,Johnny,0,0,0,,{TIME:1250240,1253330}Listen. Ayuhara's spike isn't anything like that.{NOTE:いいか。鮎原のスパイクはそうじゃないんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:56.00,Default,Johnny,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253330,1256000}She aims the ball at about this point.{NOTE:ボールがこの辺に来るところを狙うんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:57.96,Default,Johnny,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256000,1257960}Your receive isn't good either.{NOTE:レシーブだってなってないぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:21:02.92,Default,Johnny,0,0,0,,{TIME:1257960,1262920}Ayuhara's revolving receive\Nis way more amazing than you even think.{NOTE:鮎原の空中回転レシーブってのはだなお前らの考えてる以上にすごいんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:04.38,Default,Johnny,0,0,0,,{TIME:1262920,1264380}Look at this.{NOTE:いいか。見てよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:11.27,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1267890,1271270}Damn, it's nothing like Ayuhara's.{NOTE:くそ、鮎原のこんなじゃないんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.27,0:21:12.56,Default,Johnny,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271270,1272560}Virginia.{NOTE:バージニア。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:14.85,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273350,1274850}Good luck, Johnny.{NOTE:頑張ってね、ジョニー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:16.52,Default,Virginia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1274850,1276520}Bye bye.{NOTE:バイバイ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:17.69,Default,Johnny,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276520,1277690}Tsk.{NOTE:チェ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.69,0:21:19.23,Default,Johnny,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277690,1279230}Okay, the game's on!{NOTE:さ、やろうぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.23,0:21:20.15,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1279230,1280150}– Yeah!\N– Yeah!{NOTE:—おう！\\N—おう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.54,0:21:38.63,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296540,1298630}Guess I can confess to you now.{NOTE:ね、今だから白状するわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:39.25,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1298630,1299250}Hm?{NOTE:ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.25,0:21:42.55,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1299250,1302550}That last rally was really painful.{NOTE:あの最後のラリーね、本当に苦しかったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.55,0:21:46.51,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1302550,1306510}I thought to myself that it might not be possible for me to play volleyball again after that.{NOTE:それでもバレーなんて二度とできなくなるんじゃないかと思ったの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:48.26,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1306510,1308260}I was the same.{NOTE:私だって同じだったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.39,0:21:53.97,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1309390,1313970}But when we finished, I didn't feel any sense of accomplishment.{NOTE:でもね、終わった時、「あ、よくやったなー」って気持ちじゃないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.97,0:21:55.60,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1313970,1315600}"I won't lose next time."{NOTE:今度やったら負けはしない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:21:57.44,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1315600,1317440}"I want another chance, right now."{NOTE:今すぐ次のチャンスが欲しい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.44,0:21:58.85,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1317440,1318850}That's what I thought.{NOTE:そう思ったの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.85,0:21:59.86,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1318850,1319860}I see.{NOTE:そう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.86,0:22:04.61,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1319860,1324610}I thought the same after the match has ended.{NOTE:私もあの争いの終わった後の苦しい中でそう考えたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.61,0:22:06.61,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324610,1326610}When I used up my power.{NOTE:自分の力を出し切った時。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:08.45,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326610,1328450}That it's not over yet.{NOTE:それは終わりじゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.45,0:22:12.33,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1328450,1332330}That if it isn't just a beginning of another chapter in my life.{NOTE:次の新しいものへの始まりなんじゃないかしら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:14.54,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1332330,1334540}That's what I thought to myself back then.{NOTE:私はそう思ったの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.54,0:22:15.62,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1334540,1335620}Exactly.{NOTE:その通り。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.62,0:22:17.37,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1335620,1337370}– Huh?\N– Exactly what?{NOTE:—え？\\N—何なんだわ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.37,0:22:20.71,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1337370,1340710}We should play volleyball forever together.{NOTE:いつまでもみんな一緒にバレーをやってXこと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.71,0:22:22.55,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1340710,1342550}What, that's all?{NOTE:何よ、そんなことか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.55,0:22:25.13,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1342550,1345130}I thought it'd be plenty obvious by now.{NOTE:そうなの今さらXXXって当たり前のことやんか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.13,0:22:28.05,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1345130,1348050}But I see that some people in here are pretty slow.{NOTE:大きい声出して。あ、つかんだらしい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.97,0:22:36.48,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1353970,1356480}Next time we'll wipe the court with you at the Interhigh.{NOTE:今度はな、高校のインターハイでやっつけているわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.48,0:22:39.02,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1356480,1359020}Make sure you show up.{NOTE:だからちゃんと出てくれよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:41.15,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1359020,1361150}And you make sure you don't trip over your own feet.{NOTE:え、そっちらこそ気をつけて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:45.69,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1361150,1365690}That's right. I'll come and find you if you don't show up at Interhigh.{NOTE:そうよ。もしインターハイに出てこなかったら本当に叩きのめすよからね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.69,0:22:48.07,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1365690,1368070}And then, we'll come together once more…{NOTE:そして次はみんなで一緒に。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.07,0:22:49.36,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1368070,1369360}…and play at the Olympic Games.{NOTE:オリンピックよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.36,0:22:50.78,Default,Yoshimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1369360,1370780}Olympics?{NOTE:オリンピック？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.78,0:22:51.53,Default,Miyatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1370780,1371530}That's right.{NOTE:そうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.53,0:22:53.78,Default,Miyatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1371530,1373780}Our next stop is at the Olympic Games.{NOTE:次はオリンピックがあるんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.78,0:22:54.74,Default,Ootsuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1373780,1374740}Olympics.{NOTE:オリンピックね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.74,0:22:56.87,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1374740,1376870}Wow, Olympics!{NOTE:わ、オリンピック！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.87,0:23:00.62,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1376870,1380620}Exactly. Everyone has to be there. We can't lose a single person.{NOTE:そうよ。みんなで出場をするのよ。一人もかけちゃいけないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.62,0:23:03.71,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1380620,1383710}It's not going to be easy.\NThere will be lots of formidable enemies.{NOTE:厳しいわよ。強敵はいくらでもいるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.71,0:23:06.92,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1383710,1386920}But I want us to work our way through and win!{NOTE:でも、勝ち抜いて、勝ち抜いてきてほしいの。}
