Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.01,0:23:10.22,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1389010,1390220}I know we can do it.{NOTE:みんあできるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.22,0:23:11.59,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1390220,1391590}I'll do my best too.{NOTE:私も頑張るわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.59,0:23:12.89,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1391590,1392890}I'm with you.{NOTE:内もやる。}
