Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.02,0:23:17.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1397020,1397930}I'm in.{NOTE:やるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.89,0:23:19.69,Default,Miyatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1398890,1399690}Me too.{NOTE:やる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.23,0:23:21.10,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1400230,1401100}Me too.{NOTE:やる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.10,0:23:21.77,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1401100,1401770}Let's do it.{NOTE:やるぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.77,0:23:22.73,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1401770,1402730}Yeah.{NOTE:やるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.73,0:23:23.65,Default,Yoshimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1402730,1403650}Count me in.{NOTE:やるわ。}
